    <string name="help_text"><b>Navigation</b>\n
&#8226; Tap the card/press the center button to see the other side of the card.\n
&#8226; Swipe up/press the up key if you know the card.\n
&#8226; Swipe down/press the down key if you don\'t know it.\n
&#8226; Swipe right/press the right key to go to the next card.\n
&#8226; Swipe left/press the left key to go to the previous card.\n
\n
<b>Other</b>\n
&#8226; Go to Menu --> Categories to change the category.\n
&#8226; Go to Menu --> Settings to change settings.</string>

